# Repository Map

## 1. Animation Trigger Dependency Graph

### Core Animation Triggers
- `useScrollAnimation` (src/frontend/hooks/useScrollAnimation.ts)
  - Triggers: IntersectionObserver threshold (default 0.1)
  - Effects: Sets `animationPlayState: running` on target element
  - Used by: HeroSection, HowItWorksSection, EnterpriseCalloutSection, etc.

- `useScrollReveal` (src/frontend/hooks/useScrollReveal.ts)
  - Triggers: IntersectionObserver threshold (default 0.1)
  - Effects: Adds `animate-fade-rise` class and sets animation state
  - Used by: Various UI components needing scroll-triggered animations

- `NeuronCanvas` (src/frontend/src/components/NeuronCanvas.tsx)
  - Triggers: Theme changes (light/dark)
  - Effects: Renders animated neuron background based on theme mode
  - Used by: HeroSection, HowItWorksSection, EnterpriseCalloutSection

- Motion/Framer Animations
  - `HowItWorksSection`: Uses `motion` from "motion/react" for step animations
  - `EnterpriseCalloutSection`: Uses `NeuronCanvas` with theme-based animation
  - `TestimonialsSection`: Uses implicit CSS animations via classes

### Animation Dependencies
- CSS Animations: Defined in tailwind.config.js (keyframes: accordion-down/up)
- Custom Animations: Inline styles in HomePage.tsx (spin, pulse keyframes)
- Theme-Based: All animations respect dark/light mode via `useTheme` hook

## 2. Theme Variable Registry

### Design Tokens (src/frontend/lib/theme/tokens.ts)
```
colors:
  brand:
    primary: #0a0f1e (cybin-navy)
    accent: #00d4b8 (cybin-teal)
    accentWarm: #a87ef5
  dark:
    background: #0a0f1e
    surface: #110f22
    surfaceElevated: #1a1833
    heroBg: #0d1526
